Making AMQP Participants

Bootstrap
=========
Ensure the Bundler gem is installed on the system
 sudo gem install bundler
Ideally add /var/lib/gems/1.9.1/bin/ to PATH:
 PATH=$PATH:/var/lib/gems/1.9.1/bin/

Prepare .bundle/config to set the bundled_gems/ path and then:
 bundle install


Having done that we can do:
 bundle exec daemon-kit obs   -i ruote
 bundle exec daemon-kit cita  -i ruote
 bundle exec daemon-kit img   -i ruote

Now the */config/amqp.yml needs to be set

defaults: &defaults
  user: ruote
  pass: ruote
  host: amqpvm
  vhost: ruote-test

obs/bin/obs
